1. *Nogu* mu je slomio padaći sa bicikla. (He broke his leg falling from a bike.)
2. Ona je obukla crvene čizme koje su se dobro slagale sa njenom *nogom*. (She put on red boots which went well with her leg.)
3. Jedva se penjao stepenicama jer mu je bila jako bolna *noga*. (He was barely climbing the stairs because his leg was very painful.)
4. *Nogom* je otvorio vrata. (He opened the door with his foot.)
5. Ona je crtala oblike brodova *nogama*. (She was drawing the shapes of boats with her feet.)